					"text" : "This patch demonstrates a quick way to hear loudspeaker problems, in particular whether the speakers in a multi-speaker setup actually sound the same. The output of pink~ is routed to four channels of dac~ (which go to your four speakers, for example). You can easily modify this patch for a different number of outputs and then incorporate it into your concert patch as a test subpatch. For a prêt-à-porter version, check out Extras:Audiotester."
